@Gateway.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5101

### Login via gateway (Auth service: POST /api/v1/auth/login)
POST {{Gateway.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "your-password"
}

###

### Register user via gateway (Auth service: POST /api/v1/users/)
POST {{Gateway.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/users/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword1!",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

###

### Decks (requires Bearer token; policy Authenticated)
GET {{Gateway.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/decks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
